  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For others with the same name, see <a href=\"/index.php/Dickon\" title=\"Dickon\">Dickon</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Morrigen\" title=\"House Morrigen\"><img alt=\"House Morrigen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/eb/House_Morrigen.svg/50px-House_Morrigen.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/eb/House_Morrigen.svg/75px-House_Morrigen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/eb/House_Morrigen.svg/100px-House_Morrigen.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Dickon Morrigen</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Morrigen\" title=\"House Morrigen\"><img alt=\"House Morrigen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/eb/House_Morrigen.svg/50px-House_Morrigen.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/eb/House_Morrigen.svg/75px-House_Morrigen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/eb/House_Morrigen.svg/100px-House_Morrigen.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Morrigen\" title=\"House Morrigen\">House Morrigen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">Stormlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_before_Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Years before Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">2 BC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><br />south of <a href=\"/index.php/Bronzegate\" title=\"Bronzegate\">Bronzegate</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Dickon Morrigen</b> was a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Morrigen\" title=\"House Morrigen\">House Morrigen</a> during the reign of the <a href=\"/index.php/Storm_King\" title=\"Storm King\">Storm King</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Argilac_Durrandon\" title=\"Argilac Durrandon\">Argilac Durrandon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dickon_Morrigen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Dickon and the <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard_of_Blackhaven\" title=\"Bastard of Blackhaven\">Bastard of Blackhaven</a> were slain by the <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonflame\" title=\"Dragonflame\">dragonflame</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Meraxes\" title=\"Meraxes\">Meraxes</a> while leading the vanguard of Argilac during the <a href=\"/index.php/Last_Storm\" title=\"Last Storm\">Last Storm</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dickon_Morrigen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"ref